{"tid":1390240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益系列] 罷工？有乜L野用？","createTime":"2019-07-31T05:58:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T07:21:18.000Z","uid":216892,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2f782307e7a2163dd1953e827008ee2b78fe9d7b","tid":1390240,"uid":216892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:58:25.000Z","msg":"Sor 標題黨吸引大家入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小弟應該仲P牌第一次出post，但罷工單野真係唔知有咩做到，同frd傾大家都唔知點，唯有上黎問下大家，望到班義士咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />已經唔知可以做乜嘢！唯有乜鳩都諗下！<br />\n<br />\n要5/8號全城大罷工，老老柒柒，有啲難度，老闆開明嘅員工自然會罷，邊撚個有假唔想放？但老闆唔開明，同事好藍嘅，一粒小薯你叫佢力排眾議又的確唔容易！<br />\n<br />\n但係，唔好忘記，喺香港，商戶最撚驚唔係佢班員工唔返工，最撚驚係無人再幫襯！所以唔好唔記得，我哋係客人！其實我哋先係老闆！<br />\n<br />\n我哋一路叫打工仔罷工，就算一人一蚊幫襯肯罷市嘅良心企業，個效果都唔大，但其實如果倒轉諗，你唔罷市我唔撚幫襯個影響力會唔會大啲？<br />\n<br />\n諗到嘅嘢好無聊，但希望有巴絲優化下睇下可唔可行：<br />\n<br />\n1. 作為銀行存戶，<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋一人一信要求所屬銀行8月5日罷工，否則會將戶口所有錢拎走，唔好只係兇佢，要比deadline佢，如果deadline前無回應就提款！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2. 作為會去超市買嘢嘅市民，<span style=\"color: red;\">一人一信要求百佳惠康等等罷工，依家網上買嘢咁方便，唔幫襯超市都仲有好多選擇！</span><br />\n<br />\n香港作為自由經濟體系，有個優點係好多嘢都有替代品，我唔幫襯你盡對可以幫襯其他人！實際操作未諗到，但仲有幾日，希望推一推呢條戰線，由源頭開始幫呢班企業罷佢老味！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"25e230e279d12e39581e984cf1832d8864f4fffa","tid":1390240,"uid":110851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:58:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/VfuWZd5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVfuWZd5.png&h=4576ca37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1cSQ2oL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1cSQ2oL.png&h=cef8ee5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"3460272229ec04db911bb537acfe7828c9bb5192","tid":1390240,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:58:44.000Z","msg":"戒J Telegram群<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FEMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A&d=0Ti31m2ePiHoIE7ADo8qnT632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=ed8e0023\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A</a><br />\n<br />\n中醫：腎虛百病叢生<br />\n精由腎儲藏，而精既作用係用黎滋潤五臟六腑，所以丁得多會導致整個五臟六腑變差，就會出現好多症狀。"},{"pid":"ccf4e9f11df5953484e2a357aebebf9a8407600d","tid":1390240,"uid":216892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:10:43.000Z","msg":"自推兩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1685c2dac4bda7cc1d83ca00b8d899ed297ccd69","tid":1390240,"uid":216892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:11:46.000Z","msg":"再推多下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f422e7c706374c9ac3812083f76757b807b6ab73","tid":1390240,"uid":212352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:13:29.000Z","msg":"我覺得 work<br />\n每個人都真係肯做有一定威懾力"},{"pid":"2df13810dcfa814a7af28fca777146a7b87c69da","tid":1390240,"uid":120123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:16:38.000Z","msg":"罷工有用。但係唔係罷一日。<br />\n你打風夠返少日工，香港政府有冇賴屎？<br />\n要罷就要長罷。但香港工會根本呢個實力同經濟去support呢件事。"},{"pid":"f4bb73d922da19f844723b0bb1772dde4914874c","tid":1390240,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:21:18.000Z","msg":"返工但唔做野睇鏗鏘集博炒"}]}